{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"144609-sizing-things-up","title":"Sizing Things Up","description":"The world is made up of many things — big, small and middling. A small book with a big message.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"3","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Aparna  Kapur"],"illustrators":["Debjyoti  Saha"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/144609-sizing-things-up"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/300525/size3/1ae8271ff5b7dc30824b20d2844d6b57.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/300525/size6/1ae8271ff5b7dc30824b20d2844d6b57.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/196618/size6/12b459aeafc336577794e9601c25fc57.jpg","text":"The world is full\nof creatures\nand things.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/196619/size6/86b39bb8b545a50ff4a006b21e4c0ba7.jpg","text":"Some are big.\nSome are small.\nMost are somewhere in the middle.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/196620/size6/ce598cfde47bf9534e811f1dac567746.jpg","text":"These are some of the\nbiggest things we know.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/196621/size6/a1d11bc97d17e535168acfcf97fb1c73.jpg","text":"These are some of the\nsmallest things we know.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/196622/size6/2ef368683cf494058fa3be6f9df5420f.jpg","text":"Some things look big because they’re surrounded by smaller things.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/196624/size6/a2032261050852cb36934762de36e594.jpg","text":"The same things may look small when\nthey’re surrounded by bigger things.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/196626/size6/bbdf75bc535fee788075e740d9d62e11.jpg","text":"What looks big from close by,\nmay look small from far away.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/196629/size6/b5a5f28804c04426a6f40b0849f16a20.jpg","text":"Things make bigger things. Bigger things make huge ones. Huge things make ginormous ones. Ginormous things make super-duper-mega-jumbo ones.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/196630/size6/a0297f82efc420470f02f72012d83443.jpg","text":"Things are made of small things. Small things are made of smaller ones. Smaller things are made of tiny ones, which are made of eeny-teeny-weeny things.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/197241/size6/655721c100e2d38cbcc50a36f82b7c17.jpg","text":"But even the eeny-teeny-weeny can make a super-duper-mega-jumbo difference in this big-small world.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/196633/size6/bec5a27ff48e3620c91c83b4ca75c03e.jpg","text":"12/12","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":131}}